OL,4,CBBC to move key jobs and programmes out
OL,5,Cof London
OL,6, The BBC is to move some of its key
OL,7, departments and staff outside London to
OL,8, make the corporation more reflective of
OL,9, the UK as a whole.
OL,11,FIt said its plans represent a
OL,12,F"top-to-bottom change" and its biggest
OL,13,Ftransformation in decades.
OL,15,FEntire departments and news divisions
OL,16,Fwill be moved to Birmingham, Cardiff,
OL,17,FLeeds and Salford.
OL,19,FThe BBC's 22,000 employees, many of
OL,20,Fwhom are currently working from home,
OL,21,Fwere briefed on the plans on Thursday.
